name: Postcard of Beardmore Building
description:
This postcard is handmade using a photograph that is tea stained and distressed to give the appearance of a vintage image.  It is embellished with needle felted wool and stitched to a backing making it a fully functional postcard.  


Although Fiona's handmade postcards can be sent by mail as a traditional postcard would, many people choose to frame them as small works of art.  The selections available here are from a series entitled Postcards of Toronto, in which different architectural highlights of the city are featured on each card.  All of Fiona's postcards are made using her original photography.  Each one is a little different, as she chooses not to produce duplicates.

name: Hand Embellished Cashmere Sweater
description:
This sweater is one of a kind.  Made with high quality vintage cashmere and embellished with hand needle felted wool.  Size: Medium.  To prolong the life of the garment, professional dry cleaning is recommended.


If you like this sweater, but would prefer a different style, size, colour or motif placement please contact Fiona for further details:

fionakbailey@gmail.com
